long_description: The clever size 6 Nite Ize Plastic S-Biner offers a great way to manage your gear and household items with its distinctive double clip carabiner design. Dual hook design with opposing gates allow you to easily link 2 objects together. Nite Ize Plastic S-Biner features durable plastic construction and secure gate closures.
